{"tid":198503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林忌：聯航辱客的「華人迫害妄想症」","createTime":"2017-04-12T14:22:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T15:27:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce4c4754913a9bc701e396135788d27e37ba6bfa","tid":198503,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:22:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170412/56556132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170412%2F56556132&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6jCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=fea0a66e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170412%2F56556132&h=ba744519\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170412/56556132</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170412/large/1491994693_1be1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170412%2Flarge%2F1491994693_1be1.jpg&h=17671a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國的聯合航空安排混亂失當，為了安排四個職員乘搭航機，竟要求四位已通過安全檢查坐上航機的乘客「落機」，賠償安排不足以吸引乘客自願棄位，竟然強行抽籤，選中了69歲的越南移民、職業為醫生的David Dao。事發後，聯航以往辱客前科紛紛被翻出，如白人富豪原價買頭等機票，已上機在飲飛機提供的橙汁時，同樣要讓位他人，被威嚇必須下機，必要時會以手銬對付等；各國人民紛紛表示杯葛，聯合航空股價應聲下跌，除了有乘客聽到在爭辯的過程說「我被選中因為我是華裔」的道聽塗說，表面證據和種族根本無關，但華文傳媒卻把重點放在「歧視」，不少有公信力的本地傳媒，甚至把本為越南難民的事主說成是「中國人」。<br />\n<br />\n事件的重點是無論機票「超賣」，或者有突發事件要改動機位，正常的做法「先到先得」，不應趕已上機的乘客落機，或必須以重賞作賠償。沒有人自願讓位，事實說明800美元的「優惠券」沒有吸引力；另外，航空公司利用美國在9.11後反恐的安排，對一切拒絕離開機艙的乘客，以對付恐怖分子級別的暴力對待，這是濫用國家反恐來掩飾公司行政失當，這兩點才是問題的關鍵，而不是根本無關的種族歧視。<br />\n<br />\n歧視當然無處不在，例如在香港土生土長的南亞裔人，經常被當成是外人歧視；然而「華人」的問題就複雜得多，例如中國遊客在冰島破壞環境堆出「中國」字眼，在美國的官方大樓升五星旗，在泰國潑水節舉五星旗，以至把別國土生土長的華裔諾貝爾得獎者叫作「中國人」。於是「華人被迫害」變成了循環論證：首先華人當自己是「中國人」，不願融入當地社會，自稱是「華僑」，只是「僑居」於別國。但當別人也當你是中國人時，華人就高叫「被歧視」，不被當成「自己人」而是「他者」。這豈不是華人歧視自己嗎？一方面要別人不歧視你，一方面又要自視為「中國人」，這種矛盾就是「華人」的悲劇來源。<br />\n<br />\n事實上越南與中國有共同的歷史，由秦至宋都曾是中國「不可分割」的一部份。但即使越南人與華南一帶的「中國人」有血緣關係，都屬於「大中華」，但絕不能再把越南人稱為中國人，這是普世的常識。一如奧地利與德國原本都屬於「大德意志」，卻因為歷史發展，俾斯麥以普魯士為尊的「小德意志」，排除了奧地利而成立德國，雖然大家血統一樣，語言同說德文，除納粹時期外，即使奧地利人與德國人在種族上同屬日耳曼人（German），例如出生於奧地利的前美國加州州長阿諾舒華辛力加，你只能以「奧地利裔美國人」來稱呼，而絕不能稱為他為「德裔美國人」，更不能稱之為德國人或日耳曼人。這是當下文明絕不能接受的種族主義，但華人卻停留在這樣的種族主義之中，不斷高舉血統論，如諾貝爾獎就沾「傑出華人」的光，以至遇災難報道則關心有幾多「中國人」或「華人」死傷，是極為可悲的。<br />\n<br />\n（節錄，全文將於明日蘋果論壇刊出）"},{"pid":"e5519e85b1041e412a735efe6524a7bc4f2ec781","tid":198503,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:35:45.000Z","msg":"一日到黑講中國人，同納粹德國一日到黑吹日耳曼人有乜分別？<br />\n<br />\n班中國佬無料先要狐假虎威"},{"pid":"2cf66084dc6ff7697054baad833cfd897e4d8321","tid":198503,"uid":31384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:43:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一日到黑講中國人，同納粹德國一日到黑吹日耳曼人有乜分別？<br />\n<br />\n班中國佬無料先要狐假虎威</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdca2bd1714364ecb8db48fff4064fca3a4c6425","tid":198503,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:09:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1324840-20170412.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1324840-20170412.htm&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6jCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=f9e33dca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1324840-20170412.htm&h=ac46f92d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1324840-20170412.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n支那外交部指聯合航空客機事件受傷害者　為<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">越南裔美國公民</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2017-04-12 HKT 16:46<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部表示，據初步了解，被人拖出聯合航空客機的受傷害者，是<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">越南裔美國公民</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n發言人陸慷在記者會被問到，被拖走的乘客是否中國人，他作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n陸慷表示，外交部關注到這宗美國國內的不幸事件，注意到事件引發美國國內外高度關切，中方希望事件能够妥善解決。"},{"pid":"967caae697b49e1b52042f0e1459f6b7080648fb","tid":198503,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3cf93a58a8102da69e4d40c50585babf52201d","tid":198503,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T16:53:06.000Z","msg":"黑頭髮 黑眼睛 黃皮膚就係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有中國人居住地方自古以來就係中國領土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ad2aed1b4d0c7dea93617258b9269f47642547","tid":198503,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T18:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170412/photo/0412-00174-001k1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170412%2Fphoto%2F0412-00174-001k1.jpg&h=e23a9522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e3463411d4ea7c6fd24867860dac80b5061282","tid":198503,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T21:18:36.000Z","msg":"自古以來"},{"pid":"e3144894af9a91268442796764dd47ced3395c23","tid":198503,"uid":14021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T21:27:17.000Z","msg":"單嘢岀左冇耐已經有外國報導講個醫生係越南人<br />\n唔知點解香港同大陸啲報導都係話佢係華人<br />\n見Twitter 啲強國人士係咁鬧以為我地中國人好蝦乜乜乜<br />\n仲見到好似微博發起send信去白宮 話chinese lives matters <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C9Lc39gUAAEKCsp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC9Lc39gUAAEKCsp.jpg&h=324acf65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4fade758eab8507b97aaf8940ef90a2c7ca195d","tid":198503,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T21:44:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單嘢岀左冇耐已經有外國報導講個醫生係越南人<br />\n唔知點解香港同大陸啲報導都係話佢係華人<br />\n見Twitter 啲強國人士係咁鬧以為我地中國人好蝦乜乜乜<br />\n仲見到好似微博發起send信去白宮 話chinese lives matters <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C9Lc39gUAAEKCsp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC9Lc39gUAAEKCsp.jpg&h=324acf65&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n班友真係弱撚智"},{"pid":"b8929ce2cad71a114e77d7dff062a4ebecce44aa","tid":198503,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:00:08.000Z","msg":"《香港獨立論》真係神書黎:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/3yl7pwpej/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2F3yl7pwpej%2Fimage.jpg&h=b72ca977&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f3b1d8d1611584bd92440ba74138be85490a56c","tid":198503,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:00:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>單嘢岀左冇耐已經有外國報導講個醫生係越南人<br />\n唔知點解香港同大陸啲報導都係話佢係華人<br />\n見Twitter 啲強國人士係咁鬧以為我地中國人好蝦乜乜乜<br />\n仲見到好似微博發起send信去白宮 話chinese lives matters <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C9Lc39gUAAEKCsp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC9Lc39gUAAEKCsp.jpg&h=324acf65&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n班友真係弱撚智</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c5db3593fdaafe14ae790d19a7d4dd0ee0b9fd","tid":198503,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T22:17:45.000Z","msg":"聯航辱客的　華人迫害妄想症 <span style=\"color: gold;\">(續)</span><br />\n<br />\n然而，華人對自己國家認同的混亂，多少與《中國國籍法》有關。中國的政策為不承認雙重國籍，但「不承認」的意思是當你的外國國籍不存在，當你的外國護照為「旅遊證件」，即除非你能夠排除萬難成功申請「退出中國籍」，政府都當你「首先是一個中國人」。這種「不承認」與印度的不承認雙重國籍，是完全兩件事。印度的法律規定，凡印度籍人士得到外國國籍與護照，將自動喪失印度國籍，相關人士必須交出所有印度的護照與身份文件，否則將觸犯刑事法律。因此，如香港出生而得到英國公民身份的印度裔藝員喬寶寶，絕不可能同時擁有印度國籍，但中文維基百科仍然維持這種錯誤的分類，傳媒仍常把香港的南亞裔稱為「印巴籍人士」，凡見「非黃種人」則稱為「外籍人士」，是不應再犯的錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n當年越南船民來港時，即使擁有「華人血統」，也不被當「中國人」看待，不能因此而留港。David Dao由越南難民變美國人，今日香港的傳媒卻「抽水」講血統說是「中國人」，這種做法實於情於理不合，必須戒絕。"},{"pid":"b53335771ecde0c11ac2f0fba984af9e1bb4556a","tid":198503,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170412/photo/0412-00174-001k1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170412%2Fphoto%2F0412-00174-001k1.jpg&h=e23a9522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先是中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日蘋果 東方仍然話係華裔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946babf083e64e0450918da3cf370684eeb95ad7","tid":198503,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:55:16.000Z","msg":"越南自古以來是中國的"},{"pid":"2e56548961410beda9581059a5be9538b6f40f1c","tid":198503,"uid":23061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:57:37.000Z","msg":"買家甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec6abeb3f2839cb5f650ab2e3247e01fb3f9cbb2","tid":198503,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T23:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80670dde01dc07125d007f69bb93dfdaee930a5e","tid":198503,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T00:01:31.000Z","msg":"連美國當地都仲係寫緊 Asian 嘅時候，<br />\n我見到眾新聞已經寫華裔，心諗有無攪撚錯"},{"pid":"3bde716c6b227d215f19a44f524bb9deda13eab7","tid":198503,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T00:22:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買家甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買家甲寫得唔錯啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb75c9eaac76c524eb40e40c4958f03caaca4c7","tid":198503,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T00:25:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連美國當地都仲係寫緊 Asian 嘅時候，<br />\n我見到眾新聞已經寫華裔，心諗有無攪撚錯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n除非係想hint種族歧視, 否則強調族裔 (包括「亞裔」) 都係無意思的<br />\n<br />\n只係華文傳媒想借受害人散播「同仇敵慨」既大中華情花毒, <br />\n<br />\n製造香港人身份認同混亂, 令香港人覺得「華裔係外國被歧視, 大家要認做中國人, 團結一致, 唔好獨立」<br />\n<br />\n除左目的外, 我諗唔到仲有乜目的可以達到<br />\n<br />\n其實華文傳媒係食「人血饅頭」"},{"pid":"f21b86138b5413ba57d2a0006188ae8fca643fbe","tid":198503,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T00:29:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連美國當地都仲係寫緊 Asian 嘅時候，<br />\n我見到眾新聞已經寫華裔，心諗有無攪撚錯</blockquote><br />\n台灣報紙也稱亞裔"},{"pid":"625778c473c6190cad243e41726161b52cd10c72","tid":198503,"uid":84095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T00:52:20.000Z","msg":"4人隨機趕落機<br />\n仲有3 個唔講？"},{"pid":"8c32e33740453318702b8918d31165e574d25bbd","tid":198503,"uid":10937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T01:07:41.000Z","msg":"總之所謂黃皮膚黑眼睛都係華人啦<br />\n<br />\n不過咁，如果確認係日本人啦喎，睇死支那賊d報紙一定講到係個客唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef15c742b35be38aaa26688200fa4c2ceb149742","tid":198503,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T01:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>總之所謂黃皮膚黑眼睛都係華人啦<br />\n<br />\n不過咁，如果確認係日本人啦喎，睇死支那賊d報紙一定講到係個客唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以香港華文傳媒既智障程度, <br />\n連「美國籍越南華人」都UP得出, 可以自行不承認「越族」或「越裔」<br />\n(同支那國唔承認BNO係國籍一樣)<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔排除香港華文傳媒會講「美國籍日本華人」去老屈<br />\n<br />\n你知啦, 香港班妓者, 真係智力無下限架嘛！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91082799ab8190bfb9ffa7172af3cb281f9f9cef","tid":198503,"uid":23061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T02:01:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買家甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買家甲寫得唔錯啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又識抹黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}